OL,3,CTemperatures in UK could be hotter
OL,4,Cthan the Seychelles on Saturday
OL,6,FTemperatures in parts of the UK could
OL,7,Fbe higher than the Seychelles on
OL,8,FSaturday, after Britons enjoyed the
OL,9,Fhottest day of the year so far on
OL,10,FFriday.
OL,12,FThe UK will enjoy another very warm
OL,13,Fand sunny day on Saturday, with 30C
OL,14,Flikely to be recorded in the south of
OL,15,FEngland, the Met Office said.
OL,17,FThis would be higher than the
OL,18,Ftemperatures forecast in Athens in
OL,19,FGreece, Split in Croatia and even
OL,20,FVictoria in the Seychelles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
