PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779696396
OL,3,CTemperatures in UK could be hotter
OL,4,Cthan the Seychelles on Saturday
OL,6,FThe UK is also forecast to see its
OL,7,Fhottest May day on record on Monday,
OL,8,Fwith temperatures expected to reach
OL,9,F33C in southern England and the
OL,10,FMidlands.
OL,12,FBut some areas in the UK may
OL,13,Fexperience cloudier conditions on
OL,14,FSaturday, as a cold front could bring
OL,15,Fsome patchy drizzle to north-west
OL,16,FScotland, Northern Ireland and some
OL,17,Fwestern coastal regions, the
OL,18,Fforecaster said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
