FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779696396
OL,3,CTemperatures in UK could be hotter
OL,4,Cthan the Seychelles on Saturday
OL,6,FIt comes after temperatures hit 28.4C
OL,7,Fin Heathrow, Cambridge and Cranwell in
OL,8,FLincolnshire on Friday afternoon,
OL,9,Fmarking the hottest day of the year so
OL,10,Ffar.
OL,12,FThe heatwave is expected to continue
OL,13,Fover the weekend, with 31C expected to
OL,14,Fbe logged on Sunday, the Met Office
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
