PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779696396
OL,3,CTemperatures in UK could be hotter
OL,4,Cthan the Seychelles on Saturday
OL,6,FGreg Dewhurst, media adviser and
OL,7,Fsenior operational meteorologist at
OL,8,Fthe Met Office, told the Press
OL,9,FAssociation: "High pressure will
OL,10,Fdominate through the whole of the Bank
OL,11,FHoliday weekend.
OL,13,F"Plenty of very warm sunshine across
OL,14,FEngland and Wales each day.
OL,16,F"Scotland and Northern Ireland will
OL,17,Fsee more cloud at times, with a few
OL,18,Fshowers across north-west Scotland."
