PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779696396
OL,3,CTemperatures in UK could be hotter
OL,4,Cthan the Seychelles on Saturday
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,7,Fissued amber heat health alerts on
OL,8,FFriday morning for the East Midlands,
OL,9,FWest Midlands, the east of England,
OL,10,FLondon and the South East.
OL,12,FThe alerts will remain in place until
OL,13,F5pm on Wednesday and replace less
OL,14,Fsevere yellow alerts which were
OL,15,Fpreviously issued.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
