FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779696396
OL,3,CTemperatures in UK could be hotter
OL,4,Cthan the Seychelles on Saturday
OL,6,FThe alerts mean there is likely to be
OL,7,F"a rise in deaths, particularly among
OL,8,Fthose aged 65 and over or with health
OL,9,Fconditions" and increased demand on
OL,10,Fall health and social care services,
OL,11,Faccording to the UKHSA website.
OL,13,FYellow alerts have been issued for the
OL,14,Fnorth-east and north-west of England,
OL,15,FYorkshire and Humber, and the South
OL,16,FWest.
OL,18,FThe less severe alert means
OL,19,Fsignificant impacts on health and
OL,20,Fsocial care services are possible.
